    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740300/extras/50b8ea939e3984e85d2d37f4804ec6e5.poster.avif?t=1750949828\" width=606 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740300/extras/50b8ea939e3984e85d2d37f4804ec6e5.webm?t=1750949828\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740300/extras/50b8ea939e3984e85d2d37f4804ec6e5.mp4?t=1750949828\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《Smushi Come Home》是一款休闲探索冒险游戏，你将在游戏中扮演一朵尝试找到回家之路的小蘑菇！斯摩西——也就是你——忽然从家中被带走，并掉到了森林中央。虽然心中满怀迷茫与困惑，但你必须穿越森林的不同区域，在新工具和其他森林生物帮助下找到回家的路！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740300/extras/c89912c96acf873931310518c782fc8b.poster.avif?t=1750949828\" width=606 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740300/extras/c89912c96acf873931310518c782fc8b.webm?t=1750949828\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740300/extras/c89912c96acf873931310518c782fc8b.mp4?t=1750949828\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>通过奔跑、滑翔、攀爬和游泳穿越森林的不同区域！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740300/extras/ba4b05c6c7bf858eb63487958fefd2d5.poster.avif?t=1750949828\" width=606 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740300/extras/ba4b05c6c7bf858eb63487958fefd2d5.webm?t=1750949828\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740300/extras/ba4b05c6c7bf858eb63487958fefd2d5.mp4?t=1750949828\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>与你沿途遇到的古怪森林生物聊天。某些生物会向你提供帮助，而另外一些则需要你的帮助！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740300/extras/9dd66108714054fa4e0adbccb13edc06.poster.avif?t=1750949828\" width=606 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740300/extras/9dd66108714054fa4e0adbccb13edc06.webm?t=1750949828\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740300/extras/9dd66108714054fa4e0adbccb13edc06.mp4?t=1750949828\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>为了回家而体验各种冒险！部分冒险可能含有轻度平台游戏要素，而另外一些冒险则包含轻度解谜要素！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 按照自己的节奏随心探索森林的不同区域。这里没有时间限制或是游戏结束！<br></li><li> 有趣而复古的 3D 像素化美术风格，可以切换关闭或开启！<br></li><li> 进行带有轻度平台游戏要素与解谜要素的冒险！<br></li><li> 扮演一朵蹦蹦跳跳的蘑菇！！</li></ul><br>",
